overview: She is found conflicted with her dreams vs. her future? To pursue one over the other, is that really the right answer?  IS THERE really a right answer? So finally, this is it the ‘SOBRANG LAKING’ pasabog, that you all have been waiting for! Come and follow us! In the story of BULALAKAW.
tagline: Come and follow us! In the story of BULALAKAW
title: Bulalakaw
